PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the OCHAPOWACE BAND, of land situated in the Rural Municipalities of Silverwood No. 123, Willowdale No. 153 and Elcapo No. 154, Province of Saskatchewan, mines and minerals included, as follows: 59 hectares as Ochapowace Indian Reserve No. 71-27, 258 hectares as Reserve No. 71-52, 194 hectares as Reserve No. 71-64, and 129 hectares as Reserve No. 71-68.
